       </office:binary-data>
      </draw:image>
     </draw:frame>express with paint not just beauty but the feelings you have about a place, person, or thing just by manipulating colors, light, and values. Painting for me is a distraction from pain and disability, and a time of meditation that brings me great joy!</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="P179">With <text:span text:style-name="T54">my</text:span> website, my works, and my social media presence, I want to highlight how art can be beneficial as a therapy in chronic disease management (based on my experience). I hope my paintings will bring you the same happiness I felt during their creation each time they are viewed. Looking forward is easier now with a purpose, continual learning, community, and painting. </text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="P127"><text:span text:style-name="T60">Ed. Note: </text:span>See link<text:span text:style-name="T60">s</text:span> to Marla’s website in the ‘On the Internet’ section at the bottom.</text:p>
