        5x9qXMmoK8fjCBcqkWqglWS8vvEpdwMWA15j2VArwGfZqG1ovQPvzMrVqIWl6e0B0F7VAn2X
        Awk0XLqd/lHk8Pcl2j7glsHialwqQrUm+sw158zLJYA6wDb5upVql2FlnWCwMUmL67ibUuO1
        Ga8Cr7uelFaoAcW4dEE0opxccthLODyVQ8+oWlzBCtA1kJ55zGkfj9IQmIelgpvaJkKywOYx
        tRiOIBhlmWZMNFcwuT09iGR6HzACNRrYl2WalZsilLAVTqLhDG0h0qFH3rK4ZwOI1AqgU2m7
        1KExKqr6EylRa+jpBMWbhVnmdUYV1X77MQb6T//Z
       </office:binary-data>
      </draw:image>
     </draw:frame>Conveniently located within Burney Falls State Park, the Burney Falls General Store is your go-to stop for essential supplies and quick refreshments. <text:s/>You’ll find a variety of cold drinks, tasty treats, and basic camping necessities—all surrounded by the beauty of the park’s towering pines and tranquil atmosphere. Friendly staff and a rustic setting make it a welcoming stop for campers and day visitors alike.</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="P26">Ed. Note: See the link to the General Store website in the ‘On the Internet’ section at the end of this newsletter.</text:p>
    <text:h text:style-name="P177" text:outline-level="1"><text:bookmark-start text:name="__RefHeading___Toc1231_2834373222"/>Job Openings<text:bookmark-end text:name="__RefHeading___Toc1231_2834373222"/></text:h>
    <text:h text:style-name="P170" text:outline-level="2"><text:bookmark-start text:name="__RefHeading___Toc1233_2834373222"/>MBFIA Bookkeeper<text:bookmark-end text:name="__RefHeading___Toc1233_2834373222"/></text:h>
    <text:p text:style-name="P187">The Association needs a bookkeeper/treasurer to join the Board on a volunteer basis. This is a great way to give back to the community, working with a group of like-minded people who get a kick out of helping to improve three local State parks, including MacArthur-Burney Falls Memorial State Park. Great for a retired person who wants to keep active up to 10 hours a week. Knowledge of Quick Books helpful. <text:span text:style-name="T20">Contact Board President Jim Sacson at </text:span><text:span text:style-name="T24">(</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T20">530</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T24">)</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T34"> </text:span><text:span text:style-name="T20">513</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T38">‑</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T20">7102.</text:span></text:p>
    <text:h text:style-name="P200" text:outline-level="2"><text:bookmark-start text:name="__RefHeading___Toc1235_2834373222"/>Camp Hosts<text:bookmark-end text:name="__RefHeading___Toc1235_2834373222"/></text:h>
