     </draw:frame><text:s/>Here&apos;s your opportunity to contribute a tax-deductible gift to the Park and to create an everlasting memory of a special time at the park or in honor of a family member or friend, while contributing to the Friends of the Falls at the same time! Contact Bill McSweeney at: calpacker@comcast.net or 415-726-3241 for information and an application!The MBFIA builds memorial tables and places them throughout the parks. They can be purchased for $2800. Each end can have memorial information etched into the <draw:frame draw:style-name="fr5" draw:name="Image11" text:anchor-type="char" svg:x="0.0016in" svg:y="5.2307in" svg:width="3.5in" svg:height="2.6201in" draw:z-index="29"><draw:image draw:mime-type="image/jpeg">
